“I would like to provide peace of mind that you don’t have to leave the neighborhood to become your best self”

No matter what generation, we can all relate to the energy of young people going out and finding their spaces…

Domingos en Vocalo’s Rocío Santos recaps the third edition of Los Dells, one of the major celebrations of Latin music and culture in the Midwest.

We sent photographer Desmond Penn along with Matt to document all the buzz around this exciting event…

Photographer Jean Marc Lavoie was there to capture all the action from these legendary DJs, and even found a few Vocalo superfans along the way…
